data.name: _categoryTextBox.ToolTip
data.value: Enter the name of the Outlook category for filtering. If the category doesn't exist, it will be created in Outlook. If activated, only appointments belonging to that category are synced to the server.

data.name: _createInUTCCheckBox.ToolTip
data.value: Use UTC instead of Outlook Appointment Timezone for creating events on CalDAV server. Needed for GMX for example. Not recommended for general use, because recurrence exceptions over DST changes can't be mapped and Appointments with different start and end timezones can't be represented.
